response.original_title: Fred Dibnah: The Grim Reaper of the Traditional Working Man
response.overview: A young man from Bolton wrestles with his need to create something, anything, in a town devoid of opportunity. After decades of industrial decline, he focusses his ire on the one man that symbolises its end.
response.title: Fred Dibnah: The Grim Reaper of the Traditional Working Man
